{"tid":1143343,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係JENNIE] 諧星爆Jennie吃烤腸「經紀人店門口違停」　粉絲氣炸：消費BLACKPINK！","createTime":"2019-05-07T16:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T01:50:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"88b45d7ccac89cd1ceb7acf60ca9ac6e5646ff11","tid":1143343,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"南韓大勢女團BLACKPINK近日忙於全球巡演，卻又意外因捲入爭議事件。南韓諧星鄭容國（音譯，정용국）日前爆料，BLACKPINK經紀人光臨他的烤腸店時違規停車，車上還載著成員Jennie，引起粉絲認為他「消費BLACKPINK」的憤怒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4078/d4078604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4078%2Fd4078604.jpg&h=4f30dddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jennie被爆料吃烤腸時，BLACKPINK經紀人在店門口違規停車。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n鄭容國先前在廣播節目上爆料，他經營的烤腸店有回晚上11點時，來了一輛車就停在店門口，之後走下來4名工作人員，要求等等有7人要吃飯，態度也相當不好，「他們說等食物好了才會上桌，車子裡有藝人」，過了不久，Jennie就出現在店中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4078/d4078603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4078%2Fd4078603.jpg&h=45f5d4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓諧星鄭容國在廣播節目爆料。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n這段爆料引起很多討論，有人認為未遵守交通停車就是不對，但也有人緩頰：「車子不是Jennie開的，也不是她停的，經紀人的行為和她有什麼關係？」粉絲更認為鄭容國用負面消息消費BLACKPINK，對此他7日透過媒體道歉，表示：「對於我無心的言論受到傷害的人感到抱歉。」<br />\n<br />\nJENNIE係咪點滿左嘲諷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbe8dc55c5aabb6698ca2e591501f783b41f65f","tid":1143343,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"【naver】喜劇演員鄭龍國在SBS廣播節目中提到了自己家牛腸店發生的一件事。晚上11點店裡門口停了一輛黑色的保姆車，因為把車停在了違章停車區，代客停車服務生上去進行了勸阻。但是有個經紀人樣子的人說，就停這裡，貼條就貼吧。於是把車停在店門口進了飯店。接著兩個造型師兩個經紀人進來要求找一個7人的座位，還問能不能把吃的做好了再端上來。一聽就知道原來是藝人啊，把食物做好端上去，BlackPink的Jennie進來了。<br />\n<br />\n節目中這個話題只是一帶而過，但在網絡上引起大範圍爭議。一部分粉絲找到鄭龍國的ins，刷屏辱罵，要求他道歉。鄭龍國隨後通過媒體表示：向因為節目內容受到傷害的人表示歉意，自己沒有誹謗的意圖，再次致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t60lvznlj30n01ds1kx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t60lvznlj30n01ds1kx.jpg&h=040195cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t60pbumsj30n01ds1ky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t60pbumsj30n01ds1ky.jpg&h=50425778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t60tug8uj313f2dcgxl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t60tug8uj313f2dcgxl.jpg&h=308dfe1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t60vaveuj313e1vf7ro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t60vaveuj313e1vf7ro.jpg&h=4252dde7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t60i5cqmj313f2dcdtq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t60i5cqmj313f2dcdtq.jpg&h=4fc450cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t6vi2telj30990ci74f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t6vi2telj30990ci74f.jpg&h=536a032c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t6vik3zaj30940cf0st.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t6vik3zaj30940cf0st.jpg&h=ea7f6f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006YrfC3gy1g2t6vj58r0j30940cf0sv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006YrfC3gy1g2t6vj58r0j30940cf0sv.jpg&h=59c869b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47f42f08e883927819eeec2f8bb0fffa591c27d4","tid":1143343,"uid":208486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"妮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850b04a098614da96ca851b4d99b01b02cd84b0c","tid":1143343,"uid":113373,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半<br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3716e9865a89f66b022b7311680b6e9749561ac2","tid":1143343,"uid":51204,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"經紀人大哂架喎<br />\n唔覺得jennie控制到架車停係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ae179cec4bef8f2568a2262b6d12afe552b1d9","tid":1143343,"uid":88491,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"Jennie姐不嬲大牌 講事實都要比人屌 慘"},{"pid":"b86c8d008c45ead5a3c5acfcf08d1bb29fc59248","tid":1143343,"uid":251836,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"老板娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f9e7bf38e2de46e7f4bb377870437f3cb34f22","tid":1143343,"uid":201565,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:51:43.000Z","msg":"其實jennie 識道路條例咩 架車佢開架咩 好多時佢連自己去咗邊都唔知啦 到底又關blackpink 咩事 明明係yg啲人既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94729bb0c9b59b0fff2163d7ee95